        },
        "review_WjyL9m": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "image_size": 38,
            "image_size_mobile": 38,
            "image_radius": 100,
            "image_border_thickness": 2,
            "stars_count": 0,
            "stars_size": 18,
            "stars_size_mobile": 16,
            "review": "Read real reviews from our satisfied customers.",
            "stars_text": "",
            "review_custom": false,
            "review_font": "josefin_sans_n4",
            "review_size": 16,
            "review_size_mobile": 13,
            "review_height": 130,
            "review_mt": 16,
            "review_mt_mobile": 10,
            "review_color": "#121212",
            "count_color": "#121212",
            "stars_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_bg_color": "#00b67a",
            "stars_bg_half_color": "#dddddd",
            "image_border_color": "#ffffff"
          }
        },
        "slide_pcWjBG": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Screenshot_2026-03-16_at_16.43.48.png",
            "video_url": "",
            "text": "<p>Very good for the price, however difficult to tie down the seat to keep in place, so just covered the seat without straps and it fits ok, looks ok. Slip resistance could have been better. The color matches the photo too.</p>",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "badge": "",
            "author": "Barley B"
          }
        },
        "slide_pd3tWi": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Luxury_Seat_Covers_Tailored_Fit_for_Cars_SUVs_Trucks_Cognac_4.jpg",
            "video_url": "",
            "text": "<p>Love these seat covers. Very sleek look. I didn't even fasten them and they still fit very nice for my Truck. Great price. Not sure if they will get very hot in the summer time.</p>",
            "stars_count": 4,
            "badge": "",
            "author": "Amanda L"
          }
        },
        "slide_e7FJtD": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/review.svg",
            "video_url": "",
            "text": "<p>Beautiful product all the other reviews are one hundred percent correct, these seat cover fit perfect.</p>",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "badge": "",
            "author": "Tony Noseworthy"
          }
        },
        "slide_YAPaA6": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/LUXURY_SEAT_COVERS_BLACK_GREY6.jpg",
            "video_url": "",
            "text": "<p>Amazing. Made my seats look real fancy. The Napa Leather is amazing so soft and comfortable. Took about 30m to install.</p>",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "badge": "",
            "author": "Corey"
          }
        },
        "slide_66YLkw": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Premium_Waterproof_Nappa_Leather_Car_Seat_Covers_Full_Set_Universal_Fit_for_Most_Cars_SUVs_Trucks_9_1bcbabce-e6f5-4d05-8e83-3601adae578f.png",
            "video_url": "",
            "text": "<p>Took me a second to understand the straps, but after that it was smooth. Overall really happy with how they look.</p>",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "badge": "",
            "author": "Diana"
          }
        },
        "slide_mgdaxb": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/review-5.svg",
            "video_url": "",
            "text": "<p>These seat covers look like OEM. They took a little effort to install, but once they were in they look amazing.</p>",
            "stars_count": 5,
            "badge": "",
            "author": "John"
          }
        },
