    "collapsible_tabs_zdLMkX": {
      "type": "collapsible-tabs",
      "blocks": {
        "item_W67dfr": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "header": "Will these seat covers fit my car?",
            "text_size": "h4",
            "content": "<p>Yes! Our covers feature a smart, universal design that adapts to most cars, SUVs, and trucks. The adjustable straps ensure a tight, custom-like look without the annoying sliding or sagging.</p>",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "item_fYL3ma": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "header": "How easy are they to install? Do I need to take the seats out?",
            "text_size": "h4",
            "content": "<p>Installation is very straightforward and requires absolutely no seat removal or special tools. Most of our customers install the full set right in their driveway in about 30-60 minutes.</p>",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "item_hMxVfn": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "header": "What material are they made of? Is it durable?",
            "text_size": "h4",
            "content": "<p>We use premium Nappa leather—a high-grade, eco-friendly material that gives you the luxurious feel of genuine leather but is much more durable. It’s designed to withstand daily commuting, pet claws, and heavy wear and tear without cracking or peeling.</p>",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "item_wNVyPe": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "header": "Are these seat covers airbag compatible?",
            "text_size": "h4",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely. Safety is our #1 priority. The front seat covers feature specially engineered breakaway stitching. This ensures that in the event of an emergency, your side airbags will deploy instantly and safely.</p>",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "item_MUMe9B": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "header": "Can I still use my heated and cooled seats?",
            "text_size": "h4",
            "content": "<p>Yes. The premium, breathable Nappa leather allows temperature to pass through easily, so your heated and cooled seats will work just fine.</p>",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "item_gtU7Kt": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "header": "Are they easy to clean? Will they protect against spills?",
            "text_size": "h4",
            "content": "<p>Extremely easy. The Nappa leather surface is 100% waterproof. Whether it's spilled coffee, muddy paw prints, or kid messes, you can simply wipe it clean with a damp cloth. No stains, no lingering odors.</p>",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "item_NbAFmr": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "header": "What is your return policy if they don't fit?",
            "text_size": "h4",
